Are there different varieties of crops?
Are there water harvesting techniques?

54
00:03:19,229 --> 00:03:22,713
What sorts of technologies and approaches
can be brought to bear?

55
00:03:22,713 --> 00:03:26,208
And science to be underpinning them,
to be brought to bear,

56
00:03:26,208 --> 00:03:28,729
to help people cope with those things.

57
00:03:28,729 --> 00:03:30,088
If we look at sea level ri--

58
00:03:30,088 --> 00:03:34,629
I mean you can go through 
every single hazard that you can imagine,

59
00:03:34,629 --> 00:03:37,573
many of which are exacerbated 
by climate change--

60
00:03:37,573 --> 00:03:39,670
including the emergence of new disease,

61
