or re-emergence of old disease,
or pandemics--

62
00:03:42,661 --> 00:03:43,673
and there are a range

63
00:03:43,673 --> 00:03:47,791
of scientific and technological challenges
that need to be addressed.

64
00:03:47,791 --> 00:03:49,661
The Paris Agreement on Climate Change,

65
00:03:49,661 --> 00:03:54,546
the SDG, Agenda 2030 agreement
and the Sendai Framework--

66
00:03:54,546 --> 00:03:58,566
all of them have explicit roles
