67
00:03:58,566 --> 00:04:01,953
If you look at the SDGs, 
there's a section on technology

68
00:04:01,953 --> 00:04:04,822
and science and technology, 
a unique section.

69
00:04:04,822 --> 00:04:09,293
Also within many of the development goals,
the Sustainable Development Goals--

70
00:04:09,293 --> 00:04:15,427
whether it's energy, ecosystems, 
anywhere, climate change-- you see that.

71
00:04:16,917 --> 00:04:20,786
Similarly the COP, 
of course the whole IPCC process

72
00:04:20,786 --> 00:04:23,345
is fundamentally integrated with science

