75
00:04:29,366 --> 00:04:32,516
the impacts on ecosystems
and human settlements,

76
00:04:32,516 --> 00:04:34,627
these sorts of issues.

77
00:04:34,627 --> 00:04:36,347
And with Sendai as well

78
00:04:36,347 --> 00:04:40,339
there's actually a specific objective
on technological cooperation

79
00:04:40,339 --> 00:04:42,688
and the role of science is really key.

80
00:04:42,688 --> 00:04:45,777
There's a reference to the need
as part of this agreement

81
00:04:45,777 --> 00:04:48,647
to bring together 
the science and technology community

82
00:04:48,647 --> 00:04:54,000
to develop innovative solutions
to address these issues.

83
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:57,982
So number one, science and technology 
underpins all three.

84
00:04:58,662 --> 00:05:01,978
A practical-- this is maybe more 
