85
00:05:01,978 --> 00:05:04,139
but a practical integration 
between the three

86
00:05:04,139 --> 00:05:08,369
is that the SDGs, 
there's a process under way now

87
00:05:08,369 --> 00:05:11,381
to develop indicators 
