88
00:05:11,381 --> 00:05:13,630
And for the Sendai agreement, 
there's a similar

89
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:16,932
inter-governmental process 
to development indicators.

90
00:05:16,932 --> 00:05:20,340
And ISDR is ensuring 
that we don't duplicate,

91
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:24,039
that the indicators we're developing 
